Vita Mahjong is an Exclusive Puzzle Game of Tile Matching. We are thrilled to present the mahjong  game that combines innovation with classic gameplay. It offers large tiles and a user-friendly interface compatible with pads and phones. Our goal is to provide a relaxing yet mentally engaging gaming experience, particularly focused on older adults.

At Vita Studio, we have always been dedicated to crafting mobile games designed for seniors that bring back relaxation, fun, and joy. Our repertoire includes popular titles like Vita Color, Vita Jigsaw, Vita Word Search, Vita Block, Vita Sudoku, and more.

How to Play Vita Mahjong:
Playing free Vita Mahjong game is simple. Just aim to clear all the tiles on the board by matching tiles with identical images. Tap or slide two matching tiles, and they will vanish from the board. Your objective is to match tiles that are not concealed or blocked. Once all tiles are eliminated, it signifies successful completion of a majong game!

Exclusive Vita Mahjong  Game Features:
‚Ä¢ Classic Mahjong : Staying true to the original gameplay, it presents traditional card tile sets and hundreds of boards.
‚Ä¢ Special Innovations: Besides the classic, our game introduces special tiles that add a fresh twist to the classic mahjong.
‚Ä¢ Large-Scale Design: Our mahjong games feature large, easily readable text sizes to alleviate the strain caused by small fonts.
‚Ä¢ Active Mind Levels: A special mode designed to sharpen your mind and improve memory abilities in the mahjong games. 
‚Ä¢ Customizable Scoring:  You can enjoy free classic mahjong games without a timer and any score pressure.
‚Ä¢ Super Combo: When you consecutively match mahjong tiles during the game, you will unlock special experiences.
‚Ä¢ Helpful Hints: Our game provides free useful props, such as hints, undo, and shuffle, to help players overcome challenging puzzles.
‚Ä¢ Daily Challenge: Take on daily practice to collect trophies and improve your classic mahjong solitaire game skills.
‚Ä¢ Offline Mode: Full offline support lets you enjoy Vita Mahjong anytime, anywhere, without needing internet.
‚Ä¢ Multi-device: Optimized for pad and phone, ensuring everyone can enjoy the classic mahjong game.

Vita Mahjong is a versatile game made for those who love tile matching games. Download Vita Mahjong and start your mahjong dynasty now!

Note: This is a puzzle game in the style of Mahjong Solitaire. It does not contain the rules of traditional Mahjong or other types of solitaire or card games. The term ‚ÄúMahjong‚Äù here refers solely to the visual style of the tiles.

Contact us : support@vitastudio.ai
For more information, you can:
Join our Facebook group: https://www.facebook.com/groups/vitastudio
Visit our official website: www.vitamahjong.com

Conveyor‚Äôs ready, pigs are on standby. Tap to send a pig onto the conveyor so it rains balls onto pixel cubes of its own color. The number above its head is its ammo: that‚Äôs how many hits it makes. Run out and it leaves the stage; if not, it slips into one of the 5 waiting slots and, when you tap again, it jumps back on the conveyor to fire another round.
The conveyor has a capacity‚Äîpush past the limit and you‚Äôll need to wait. Send them in the right order, manage the flow, and hit the cubes to clear the board piece by piece. Simple mechanic, sticky loop: tap ‚Üí flow ‚Üí repeat.
Highlights
One-tap control: Quick sessions, easy one-handed play.
Color matching: Pigs only hit their own color‚Äîno target-picking hassle.
Conveyor capacity: Timing and queue management add a bite-size strategy layer.
5 waiting slots: Stack, sort, and launch at the perfect moment.
Short but ‚Äúone more round‚Äù feel: Perfect for micro-breaks.
Satisfying pixel cleanup: Every hit leaves the board feeling crisp.
For anyone who loves fast action-puzzles, timing, and flow management. The pigs are ready. The cubes‚Ä¶ not so much.

data.app_description:
Kingshot is an innovative idle medieval survival game that combines strategic gameplay with rich details waiting to be explored.

When a sudden rebellion overturns the fate of an entire dynasty and ignites a devastating war, countless people lose their homes. In a world riddled with societal collapse, rebel invasions, rampant disease, and mobs desperate for resources, survival is the ultimate challenge. As a governor in these turbulent times, it's up to you to lead your people through these adversities, devising internal and diplomatic strategies to rekindle the spark of civilization.

[Core Features]

Defend Against Invasions
Stay vigilant and ready to repel invasions at any moment. Your town, the last bastion of hope, depends on it. Gather resources, upgrade your defenses, and prepare for battle to ensure survival in these tough times.

Manage Human Resources
Enjoy a unique gameplay mechanic involving the allocation of survivor roles such as workers, hunters, and chefs. Monitor their health and happiness to ensure they remain productive. Respond quickly to illness to make sure everyone receives timely treatment.

Establish Laws
Codes of law are vital for sustaining civilization and are crucial for the growth and strength of your town.

[Strategic Gameplay]

Resource Struggle
Amidst the sudden state collapse, the continent is flooded with untapped resources. Refugees, rebels, and power-hungry governors are all eyeing these precious materials. Ready yourself for battle and use every strategy at your disposal to secure these resources!

Battle for Power
Compete against other players for the ultimate honor of becoming the strongest governor in this grand strategy game. Claim the throne and reign supreme!

Forge Alliances
Ease the burden of survival in this chaotic world by forming or joining alliances. Collaborate with allies to rebuild civilization!

Recruit Heroes
The game features a roster of unique heroes, each waiting to be recruited. Bringing together heroes with various talents and skills is essential for taking the initiative and ensuring safety in these desperate times.

Compete with Other Governors
Hone your heroes' skills, assemble your squads, and challenge other governors. Victory not only earns you valuable points, but also grants access to rare items. Lead your town to the top of the rankings and showcase the rise of a great civilization.

Advance Technology
With the rebellion obliterating almost all technological advancements, it's crucial to start rebuilding and reclaiming the fragments of lost tech. The race to master cutting-edge technology could determine the dominator of this new world order!

data.app_description:
Combine the photos on the cards correctly to complete a single picture. Once you experience the satisfying snap of the cards fitting perfectly, you'll be hooked for sure!

[Game Features]
- Enjoy Completing Photos by Combining Cards
Even if the cards seem random at first, finding the exact spot they fit brings unmatched satisfaction!

- Intuitive Swipe Controls
Simply swipe to move the cards. When cards stick together, you can move them as a group, making gameplay smooth and easy.

- Exhilarating Chain Reactions
The thrill of multiple cards locking into place all at once is seriously addictive. This is a puzzle game with high replay value.

- Designed for All Skill Levels
Whether you have a bit of free time or want a longer play session, this game is perfect. You'll find new discoveries each time you play!

- Wide Variety of Themed Photos
From flowers and landscapes to animals, we plan to continuously add a diverse range of photos!

[How to Play]
- Swipe to Move Cards
Swipe your screen to drag the cards wherever you like.

- Move Connected Cards All at Once
When cards are placed correctly, they snap together. You can then move the connected group of cards as a single unit.

- Caution When Overlapping Large and Small Cards
If you place a small card on top of a larger one, the larger card may shrink. Pay close attention to any size changes and combine them carefully.

Despite its simple controls, "Jigsolitaire" offers depth through strategic card placement. Whether you love jigsaw puzzles, enjoy solitaire, or just want a fun and easy puzzle, give it a try!

Enjoy the best free and popular original Solitaire card games in the world for free at any time and place! It's time to train your brain, challenge yourself and be a Solitaire or Patience master, try this original, classic and free Patience Solitaire card game!

Solitaire games, also known as Patience in Europe (such as the United Kingdom, French, etc.), are Solitaire card games, and can be played by a single player. 

This is not a social casino game. You can enjoy original Solitaire anytime and anywhere, without money in and money out.

How to play this free original solitaire card games
To solve this FREE Solitaire card puzzle, you should move all solitaire cards of 4 suits - hearts, diamonds, spades and crosses to the Solitaire Foundations. There is one deck - 52 solitaire cards in the classic Solitaire game. 

You need to stack solitaire cards by suit, from Aces to King (A, 2, 3 and more). You can also move solitaire cards between columns, and stack solitaire cards in descending order and differentiate between red and black suits. Dive into the laugh-out-loud world of Lamar, a vlogger determined to turn life's challenges into viral opportunities. In this engaging idle clicker and life simulator, watch Lamar transform from zero to hero, making his way to the top as a rich tycoon in the influencer industry.
From Cheated to Champion
Lamar‚Äôs journey kicks off with a shocking revelation: he was cheated. But instead of giving up, he decides to start his vlogging career. His mission? To go from an unknown, struggling individual to a viral vlogger and rich tycoon, proving that with grit and creativity, anyone can achieve greatness.
Vlogger Go Viral
Create content that captures the hearts of millions. Experiment with hilarious pranks, engaging challenges, and viral trends to build a massive fanbase. Your goal is simple: make Lamar the most famous vlogger on the internet. As an idle streamer, even when you're not actively playing, Lamar's channel continues to grow, attracting more fans and generating more revenue.
Build Your Empire

Transform your humble beginnings into a luxurious lifestyle and become a true rich tycoon in the influencer world. Life Simulator and Beyond

From planning content to dealing with haters, every decision you make impacts Lamar‚Äôs journey. Collaborate with other influencers, participate in trending challenges, and unlock exciting new opportunities as you climb the ladder of fame.
Interactive Gameplay

Associations - Colorwood Game is a beautifully crafted association game that invites you to slow down and think creatively. 

Each level presents a curated puzzle of words that may seem unrelated ‚Äî until you begin to notice the hidden logic beneath them. Calm yet clever, the game is designed for those who love language, pattern recognition, and a satisfying ‚Äúaha‚Äù moment.

Whether you're enjoying a quick brain teaser or diving into a longer session, Associations - Colorwood Game delivers a relaxed yet engaging experience. Let your intuition lead the way as you uncover thematic links and build meaning from apparent chaos.

Key Features:

Elegant word association gameplay
This is not about guessing definitions ‚Äî it's about discovering connections. Each level challenges you to group related words by theme. Some links are simple. Others might surprise you. But each one rewards insight and creative thinking in a way only a true word association game can.

Extra layers of challenge
As you master the basics, new elements appear that add complexity and variety. These extra touches make every session feel fresh and full of discovery ‚Äî keeping even experienced players intrigued.

Thoughtful hint system
Need a nudge in the right direction? Use the adaptive hint feature to highlight possible connections and get back on track ‚Äî without breaking the flow.

Perfect for fans of language puzzles, logic games, or just a peaceful mental workout, Associations - Colorwood Game is a refined word game that invites you to pause, reflect, and enjoy the small delight of connecting words.

Perfect for fans of tile games and brain puzzles, Hexa Sort Challenges your mind with stimulating brainteaser games that involve clever puzzle solving and logical maneuvers, making it an ideal choice for those seeking a mental workout. 
 
Hexa Sort introduces a unique twist to the classic sorting puzzle concept, inviting players to explore the art of shuffling, connecting, matching and organizing hexagon tile stacks. With the goal of achieving color matches, players can dive into the excitement of challenging puzzles and enjoy the calming effects of tile stacking brainteasers for adults. Each level presents challenges to meet collection goals, providing a perfect balance of excitement and stress relief for those who prefer relaxing casual games.

Turn the tide and win the war in this elegantly simple casual tactics game that‚Äôs guaranteed to appeal to all armchair commanders and pocket Napoleons. Head into battle with a single üëâ swipe and watch your little warriors eliminate the enemy, allocating your cute little forces with skill and precision to maintain your position and overcome the opposing armies.

‚òÖ Hours of towers! Use your tactical cunning to progress through the levels of tower-defense and unlock new types of towers, including artillery posts and tank factories. Other game mechanisms including multiple enemies, barriers, blockades, and mines mean the war is never over and there‚Äôs always a new challenge to spice up the already massively addictive gameplay.

‚òÖ Towering achievements ‚Äì keep finding the elegant tactical solutions to win each battle so that you can unlock new areas and continue your reign of conquest in new climes, with beautiful backdrops adding to the game‚Äôs already supremely elegant (and cute) design.

ALL YOUR TOWERS ARE OURS! üéñÔ∏è

Dear players, our game is under active development! We ask you to write your wishes and suggestions, what you would like to see in the next update.

School Party is a cubic style life simulator for schoolchildren and teenagers.
You have a big city at your disposal, in which there are many cute girls and nice boys.
You not only have to hang out and do shopping, but also buy mansions, meet cool characters and even ride the coolest cars!
In this city, your possibilities know no boundaries: building houses, buying blocks, furniture and doors is just the beginning of a big adventure.
Be trendy and stylish - dress up, walk around town, swim in the pool, go to the movies and dance in the crazy disco!

Crafting and building:
Many beautiful mansions with large plots where you can demolish the purchased house and build the cottage of your dreams.
A large collection of various blocks for construction and decoration.
Hundreds of types of furniture for every taste: chairs, tables, sofas and beds, wardrobes and more.
Doors, houseplants and chandeliers will complete the design of your home.

Relationship between players:
Don't worry, you are not alone in the city.
There are thousands of people in the city with whom you can communicate, be friends, walk together, visit a restaurant and a park, ride supercars together and hang out in a nightclub.
If you like the character, add him to the phone book and communicate with him via SMS at any time.

Paintball:
Large selection of paintball weapons:
Miniguns, Pistols, Assault Rifles and exclusive Dinogun, Bazooka-Shark and more.
All this shoots colored bullets with paints.
Shoot the hooligans who took your coins and they will return them to you.

Interesting places:
- Market (furniture, blocks, doors, skins and paintball guns)
- Disco (order music from DJs and dance with your friends)
- Large park
- Beach and sea with sun loungers
- Restaurant and cinema
- School and bank
- Car dealership and gas station
- City pool

Features of the game:
- Driving cars and tuning
- Sport: motorcycles, bicycles, scooters and skateboards
- Mini-games (barman in the disco (2nd floor), barman in the restaurant (1st floor), game of smiles)
- Chests with coins and many bonuses
- Ship cruise and airplane flight
- Swimming (on the beach and in the pools)
- Beautiful character animation
- First and Third person camera
- Interactive with furniture (sit, sleep etc)
- Change of weather and time of day
- Convenient and intuitive controls
- Optimization for weak devices (from 1 GB of RAM)
- Customization of gameplay and buttons to your liking

Create your pixel interior in the world of fairy tales and fantasy.
Enjoy your game.

Get ready for an exclusive and original Mahjong Solitaire game! Vigor Mahjong combines innovation with classic gameplay of Tile Matching, meticulously crafted for the senior audience. It offers large tiles and a user-friendly interface compatible with pads and phones.

Escape in the tranquil beauty of Vigor Mahjong where hundreds of tile matching puzzles are ready to solve in this popular game of strategy, memory, and skill. Our goal is to provide a relaxing yet mentally engaging gaming experience, particularly focused on older adults.

How to Play:
The goal of the game Mahjong Solitaire is to remove all the Mahjong tiles on the board by matching pairs of Mahjong tiles. Tap or slide two matching tiles, and they will disappear from the puzzle board. You can only remove majong tiles that are free and not covered. When all tiles are removed from the board, it signifies successful completion of a mahjong game!

Vigor Mahjong Features:
- Immerse yourself in breathtaking graphics and beautifully crafted tile designs that staying true to the original gameplay.
- Large, easily readable font sizes to alleviate the strain caused by small texts.
- From classic layouts to unique puzzles, Vigor Mahjong offers over 20,000 levels to keep you entertained for hours.
- Choose your own score system: no timer, no pressure.
- When you consecutively match mahjong tiles during the game, you will unlock special combos.
- Use HINTS or SHUFFLE tiles for ease of play. Earn extra points when you solve puzzles without help.
- Special daily challenges available for you to complete each day.
- No Wifi, no problem! Play offline if you wish.

Play among gorgeous backgrounds, relaxing sounds, and unique themes to match any mood in Vigor Mahjong now!

Feeling stressed? Relax and enjoy a fun challenge with Daily Number Match ‚Äì a perfect combination of entertainment and logic puzzles.

Daily Number Match is a fun and addictive number-matching puzzle game that sharpens your mind and provides hours of entertainment! Match numbers and clear the board while exercising your logic, math skills, and focus. Play thousands of free number puzzles that test your logic and math abilities, all while having fun! üî¢

If you're looking for a simple, engaging puzzle experience, Daily Number Match offers an easy-to-learn, logic-based math game that lets you focus on solving puzzles and having fun.

‚ú® How to Play:
- The goal is to clear all the numbers from the board.
- Find pairs of the same number or pairs that sum to 10 (e.g., 6 & 4, 8 & 2) on the puzzle grid.
- Check each row, column, and diagonal for pairs. As long as no numbers are between them, they can be eliminated!
- Clear one row to shift up the remaining numbers and create new pairs
- If no pairs are left, click "+" to copy the remaining numbers and create more pairs
- Win by clearing all the numbers from the number puzzle grid.

‚ú® Features:
- Simple & Addictive Gameplay: Tap on the numbers to eliminate them and clear the board. Easy to learn but challenging to master!
- Infinite Play: Over 10,000+ stages with new puzzles added regularly, ensuring you'll never run out of challenges.

- Daily Challenges & Rewards: Complete daily challenges, earn generous rewards, and track your progress. Special seasonal events to collect exclusive postcards!
- Helpful Hints: Stuck on a puzzle? Use hints to help you find the next pair and keep going.
- Designed for All Players: Suitable for beginners and experts alike with levels that match all skills
- Play Anytime & Anywhere: No time limits, no wifi needed! Enjoy the game at your own pace.

‚ú® Why You'll Love Daily Number Match:
- Great Brain Workout: Enjoy free logic games and number puzzles while exercising your brain.
- Relaxing & Rewarding: No stress or time limits‚Äîjust fun and rewarding number puzzles to help you relax and unwind.
- Become a Number Match Master: Challenge yourself to clear the board and beat your high score. 

Daily Number Match is a challenging logic puzzle game designed to meet all your expectations. üíØ If you are a math puzzle fan looking for a free, pure math puzzle game without annoying features, then Daily Number Match is definitely for you! üéØ

Welcome to the heart of the Midwest, where vast fields, charming farmsteads, and a deep mystery await! This farming simulator expands the Big Farm franchise with Big Farm: Homestead! 

In Big Farm: Homestead, you face the challenge of restoring the three Townsend family farms; each with its own unique crops, animals, and history. This engaging farming sim is more than just a farming game, it's a story of discovery: once-thriving White Oak Lake, the village's water source, is draining, and pollution is spreading. Someone is behind this disaster, and it's up to you to uncover the truth in this rich farm story!

BUILD & EXPAND YOUR BIG FARM

Your journey in this relaxing simulation game is all about growth. Grow a variety of crops, from golden wheat and juicy corn to specialty Midwestern produce. Harvest plentiful resources daily to sustain your big farm.  Raise adorable animals including cows, horses, chickens, and even rare breeds!

Upgrade your barns, silos, and farmhouses to create a thriving agricultural empire. Every piece of equipment plays a part in the prosperity of your farm city as you build your ultimate homestead. It‚Äôs the perfect blend of a gentle farming simulator and an exciting farm tycoon experience.

EXPERIENCE TRUE FARMING LIFE IN YOUR VILLAGE

Immerse yourself in the rhythm of village life. Harvest fresh produce, craft delicious goods, and fulfill orders to help local townsfolk. 

Join the community of dedicated farmers who make this farming region so special. This is one of the best farm games for free that lets you live out your dream of successful farming.

SAVE THE LAKE & UNCOVER THE MYSTERY

The lifeblood of these farms - the beautiful White Oak Lake - is vanishing. Who is behind it? Follow a captivating story, interact with interesting characters, and solve the game's mystery before it‚Äôs too late!

MAKE THE FARM BEAUTIFUL

Decorate your farm with charming fences, orchards, flowerbeds, embodying the American farming spirit in your own homestead. 

MEET FARMING CHARACTERS

Form friendships, unlock new storylines, and work with other farmers in the village to rebuild the Townsend legacy. Your family and friends are integral to your journey in this warm-hearted farm story.

COMPLETE QUESTS & EXPLORE NEW ADVENTURES

Take on exciting farm challenges, seasonal events, and hidden treasures as you expand your farming skills! Embark on an adventure that transforms your small plot into a bustling, dream big farm.
The future of the Townsend's farms and the lake rests in your hands. Can you restore the farms, save the water, and uncover the secret behind the destruction?

Start your American farming simulator adventure today in Big Farm: Homestead, the game that turns farming into a thrilling harvest adventure! 
Experience the joy of harvest land and build your dream farm village simulator in one of the top free farming games available. This farm story is your chance to build a legacy, not just a ranch!

Summon over 800 legendary heroes from 15 factions to battle bosses like fearsome dragons and colossal demons. Explore dungeons, enjoy turn-based multiplayer action, and master tactics to free Teleria in this epic role-playing game!

Tactical battles await in this turn-based dark fantasy role-playing game, where you can summon hundreds of Champions from 15 playable factions.

Fight the forces of the dark lord Siroth with your legendary band of immortal warriors. Train them for battle, craft the perfect strategy, and assemble the greatest raiding party ever seen.

Epic clashes await in online modes like the multiplayer Arena, where you can put your team of Champions against others in strategic RPG battles. Experiment with over 1+ million possible Champion builds, craft the ultimate team and their battle tactics, and be the best!

With over 5 years of free content updates and a community that grows bigger every day, join millions of players in the war to liberate Teleria from Siroth and his legions. Become a hero of legend!

| Enjoy deep RPG features |

Collect powerful Champions
Summon 800+ warriors from 15 factions in this tactical role-playing game. Call upon orcs, knights, elves, and more dark fantasy creatures to defeat any threat that stands in your way.

Strategic turn-based RPG gameplay
Equip your Champions with amazing artifacts to aid them in battle. Rank them up to unleash devastating skills, AOE attacks, magic powers and more as you lead them in combat.

Fight epic boss battles
Do you dare take on the Magma Dragon, the Fire Knight, or the Ice Golem? Vanquish challenging bosses in dangerous dungeons for loot, XP, and special Champion drops. Then, in classic turn-based RPG style, fight them again for more powerful gear!

Feel the visceral 3D artwork
Beautiful, fully-rendered 3D heroes offer stunning detail down to the cracks in their armor. Marvel at a vivid fantasy world with thousands of unique skill and attack animations.

Join forces with your Clan
Team up with fellow players and take on challenges like the fearsome Demon Lord with Clans! Battle other Clans in special tournaments and show them that they‚Äôre out of your league.

Face the multiplayer PvP Arena
Go head-to-head with other players in fierce turn-based combat to unlock special gear. Rise through the ranks and become an Arena legend.

Develop and manage your Bastion
Upgrade your own personal fortress to manage your Shards and ready your Champions for dungeon runs, multiplayer arena combat, and the story campaign.

Clear our massive PvE Campaign map
Experience epic dark fantasy done right through 12 spectacular RPG locations spread over a sprawling, fully-voiced story campaign. Heed your heroic duty and conquer the forces of Darkness.

Dive into a deep fantasy world
Learn about Teleria‚Äôs heroes and villains with our growing collection of Champion bios. Then, check out our animated limited series, RAID: Call of the Arbiter, on YouTube!
